  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CHOOSE YOUR EQUIPMENT</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >RuneLight has dozens of powerful and game changing equipment pieces to collect. Swap out, mix, and match equipment to make a wide variety of builds and synergies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393910/extras/5b89e3b23f0eaa374fb754f960a502cd.avif?t=1740284184\" width=532 height=218 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BUILD YOUR WEAPON</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >RuneLight is all about crafting powerful builds, and allows you to customize your weapon's stats to match it. With dozens of weapon modifiers increasing a variety of stats, you can make your weapons fit your own needs<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393910/extras/93761af51b5c4bb316a57de7a7f86ad2.avif?t=1740284184\" width=532 height=218 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393910/extras/cbf09dc7d7d012ff7fc98899a65e1529.poster.avif?t=1740284184\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393910/extras/cbf09dc7d7d012ff7fc98899a65e1529.webm?t=1740284184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393910/extras/cbf09dc7d7d012ff7fc98899a65e1529.mp4?t=1740284184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DISCOVER FUSIONS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each equipment piece can be fused into one of two paths. Double down on powerful items, discover new synergies, and perfect your build</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\